<whdroplet name="drDemoSetupHTQ1">
<ol>
<li> Requires whQuery1.exe </li>
<li> The Borland Database Engine is required</li>
<li> The tables "contract.db" and "member.db" are required (included).</li>
<li> The table navigation is defined through a combination of answergrid.Captions, 
answergrid.ButtonSpecs, and Cascading Style Sheet entries.</li>
</ol>
