<whtranslation key="~whDemoShortDescHTQ1">
This web application demonstrates (a) how to run a query that leads to an HTML table result;
(b) how to make the query selected based on data typed in by a site visitor; and 
(c) how to show an error message if the query returns zero records.
</whtranslation>

<whtranslation key="~whDemoLongDescHTQ1">
The query will select all matches for the MemberID, as long as the correct 
password is supplied.
</whtranslation>

